wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.4/Python-3.7.4.tar.xz

Now we need to unzip the file using below commands:
tar -xJf Python-3.7.4.tar.xz

Let us navigate to the folder and use configure command to install the package:
cd Python-3.7.4
./configure

Let us compile the program using make command and then install the python:
make
make install

